      "description": "Supplemental experimental hemolysis measurements collected after the initial package was signed and submitted. Data from two additional pump operating points (4 L/min at 3200 RPM and 5 L/min at 3400 RPM) were incorporated to strengthen the output comparison factor. Package was updated post-signing to include this evidence without re-signing the UnitOfAssurance. Predicted NIH values fall within ±18% of measured values across all seven operating points.",
