      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test samples must be characterized for variability; inter-sample variability in blood properties must be documented.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data does not report inter-sample variability in blood properties or pump-to-pump geometric variability. Factor not formally assessed. Achieved level 1."
    },
