      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in the validation study must be demonstrated equivalent to those in the COU; species differences in blood rheology must be formally addressed.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood rheological parameters used in validation; human blood parameters assumed equivalent without formal equivalency analysis. This is a critical gap at MRL 5 for a Class III device. Factor not assessed. Achieved level 1."
