    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package based on the supplemental experimental comparison data (added post-signing) which narrowed the output comparison uncertainty. The team noted the package was updated post-signing to incorporate the additional hemolysis measurements without re-signing, and accepted this on the basis that the supplemental data was considered confirmatory rather than substantive. This decision is flagged as potentially inconsistent given the unsigned post-signing evidence update.",
